body_html:
@shallam66 I noticed that you are using the tensorflow serving protos with tensorflow protos. I had a similar issue when compiling protobufs when making a minimalist repo.

https://github.com/Ouwen/minflow_serve_proto

In this repo are the protos from tensorflow set in the original tree structure. I had to add
option go_package to all of .proto files which did not already have it.

Let me know if this fits what you are trying to do.

body:
@shallam66 I noticed that you are using the tensorflow serving protos with tensorflow protos. I had a similar issue when compiling protobufs when making a minimalist repo.

https://github.com/Ouwen/minflow_serve_proto

In this repo are the protos from tensorflow set in the original tree structure. I had to add
`option go_package` to all of `.proto` files which did not already have it.

Let me know if this fits what you are trying to do.
